  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with histologically confirmed MALT lymphoma with measurable disease (stage
             I-IV)

          -  with first or greater relapse after HP-eradication, radiation or chemotherapy ,

          -  age &gt; 18 years

          -  must be able to tolerate therapy and have adequate cardiac, renal and hepatic function

          -  ECOG status of &lt;_ 2

          -  must be capable of understanding the purpose of the study and given written informed
             consent
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
